'''''King Solomon's Mines''''' ni film yasohotse muri 1985 , iturutse kuri novel yitwa <nowiki><i><b>King Solomon's Mines</b></nowiki><nowiki></i></nowiki> yanditswe na  H. Rider yajonjogoye . Irimo Richard Chamberlain, Sharon Stone, Herbert Lom na John Rhys-Davies . Yahinduwe na Gene Quintano na James R. Silke kandi iyobowe na J. Lee Thompson . Iyi verisiyo yinkuru yari yoroheje,  urwenya, iganisha ku  gusebya ''Indiana Jones'' (aho umukinnyi wa francise Rhys-Davies yagaragaye mubice bibiri). Yafatiwe amashusho hanze ya [[Harare]] muri [[Zimbabwe]] . <ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0089421/locations?ref_=tt_dt_dt</ref>

Yakurikiwe nuruhererekane ''[[:en:Allan_Quatermain_and_the_Lost_City_of_Gold|Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold]]'' (1986) kandi yagombaga gukurikirwa nuruhererekane rutigeze rukorwa: igerageza ry'ambere ryaba rishingiye kuri ''She na Allan'', ikindi gitabo cya Haggard, hanyuma kugerageza bwa kabiri kwitwa ''Allan Quatermain na Jewel of the East'' kandi iyobowe na producer Golan.

